            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">7. A 65-year-old Hispanic man is seen in the office for follow-up. He was placed on metformin for type 2 diabetes after not responding to<br />\nmodifications of diet and exercise several months ago. Despite maximal doses of metformin, his blood glucose is > 150 mg/dL and HgA1c is above 7 percent. What is the next best step in management?</p>"
